prodNameC: 羅氏可霸斯免疫分析促腎上腺皮質激素檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagents - working solutions
M Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 6.5 mL: Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL; preservative.
R1 Anti-ACTH-Ab~biotin (gray cap), 1 bottle, 8 mL: Biotinylated monoclonal anti-ACTH antibody (mouse) 0.3 mg/L; MESb buffer 50 mmol/L, pH 6.2; preservative.
R2 Anti-ACTH-Ab~Ru(bpy)2+3 (black cap), 1 bottle, 8 mL: Monoclonal anti-ACTH antibody (mouse) labeled with ruthenium complex 0.3 mg/L; MES buffer 50 mmol/L, pH 6.2; preservative. 

CalSet – working solutions
• ACTH Cal1: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
• ACTH Cal2: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
ACTH (synthetic) in two concentration ranges (approx. 15 pg/mL and approx. 120 pg/mL) in an equine serum matrix.

PreciControl - working solutions
• PC ACTH1: 2 bottles, each for 2.0 mL of control serum
• PC ACTH2: 2 bottles, each for 2.0 mL of control serum
ACTH (synthetic) in two concentration ranges (approx. 100 pg/mL and
approx. 1000 pg/mL
